    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It has significant mechanical issues and will require substantial repairs before it can be driven reliably. The exterior shows considerable wear including scratches, dents, and paint damage. The interior is also worn with visible damage to surfaces and components. This vehicle is best suited for someone prepared to invest in repairs or use it for parts.",
      "price": 7000.0,
